HEADWORD: Exposedness
<hw>Ex*pos"ed*ness</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The state of
being exposed, laid open, or unprotected; <as>as, an
<ex>exposedness</ex> to sin or temptation</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
